_sText:
Pretty much a basic aim_ map, base to base fighting.
Every round there is a 50% chance to start with ak and a glock or colt and a usp.
2 deagles in this map and 1 awp as well. You lose the awp at the start of next round. 
Oh, and you can shoot through the covers with the awp.
---------------------------
Contains a .nav file but the map is not supposed to be played with bots.
